Package edu.cnm.deepdive.northstarsharingclient.model

Class Gallery

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.northstarsharingclient.model.Gallery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    public class Gallery
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Encapsulates a persistent gallery object with: title, description, Href location, reference to the creating User, and reference to the {@link List<Image>}.
